item.description: Guoyi Zhu is an System Operation Engineer for open source. He has a solid experience in the middleware and information technology industry for more than 5 years. He loves open source, including kubernetes、docker、linux, etc. He also has strong interests in various tech stuff such as Artificial Intelligence, Storage, Smart Home. He worked in HUAWEI for 3 years. He is happy with his current job, but also willing to take new challenges if the opportunity matches his career path.
